Yeɛya werwiḥ!
Ur iban ara ssuq-is.
Anda yedda d leɛnaya.
S anda ara terreḍ?
Yuɣal-d zik si lexla ass-a.
Ifka-t inijjel i lexla.
Ruḥ ad twaliḍ.
Azzel ad d-tawiḍ.
Azzel neɣ qqim!
Yeǧǧa-t di tazzla.
Ǧǧan-aɣ gar yiberdan.
Ddiɣ d yir arfiq, yeǧǧa-yi deg yir amḍiq.
Tin i d-yeddan d tin!
Ur d-yeddi ara deg wawal.
Yeṭṭerḍeq waɛbar.
Ijba-d di tiɣilt.
Yebra-d lmal.
Tebra-d i lmal.
Yebra-d i leɛǧeb.
Yebra i yimeẓẓuɣen-is.
Yugi ad yekker.
Ugin ad kkren.
Kkrent tmeccacin n wemɣar.
Wwet-as ad tekker!
Tekker deg uzagur-is.
Tekker teqcict-a deg yiwen n wass!
Yekker ubaxix!
Yeggull deg-i.
Ay agejdur, a tasilt!
Taqbaylit mačči d urar.
Taqbaylit mačči d iḥulfan kan.
Aṭas i yestehzayen di tira s teqbaylit.
Berka astehzi!
Akken i txedmeḍ ad ak-ittwaxdem.
Ur kkat ara deg wiyaḍ.
Ulac win i d-ikkren yessen.
Tgerrez tsuqilt-a!
Nniɣ-d ayen i walaɣ.
Nehhren-t medden am uɣyul.
Ur yessin ara ad inher.
Ur ssineɣ ara ad nehreɣ.
Ur tessineḍ ara ad tnehreḍ ula d aɣyul.
Melmi kan i bdiɣ tanhert.
Melmi i tebdiḍ tanhert?
Melmi i tebdam tanhert?
Melmi i tebdamt tanhert?
Melmi i yebda tanhert?
Zik i bdiɣ tanhert.
Werǧin nehreɣ takerrust.
Yugi-yi baba ad nehreɣ takerrust-is.
Yugi-yas baba-s ad inher takerrust n gma-s.
Ttkukruɣ ad nehreɣ takerrust.
Tettkukru ad tenher.
Ur tnehher ara tmeṭṭut-iw.
Iḥar mmi melmi ara yenher takerrust.
Ur zmireɣ ara ad nehreɣ deg yiḍ.
Tettaggad ad tenher deg yiḍ.
Ur ttɣawaleɣ ara di tenhert.
Inehher s tɣawla.
Tanhert-is d tazwawaṭ.
D učči i ttetteḍ abrid mi ara tnehhreḍ.
D učči i tetten abrid mi ara nehhren.
Ur iṣeḥḥa ara yiẓri-w i tenhert.
Ur iṣeḥḥa ara yiẓri-k i tenherk.
Ur iṣeḥḥa ara yiẓri-m i tenhert.
Ur iṣeḥḥa ara yiẓri-is i tenhert.
Laqent-iyi nnwaḍer i tenhert.
Laqent-ak nnwaḍer i tenhert.
Laqent-am nnwaḍer i tenhert.
Acḥal aya ur nhireɣ.
Acḥal aya ur tenhireḍ waqila?
Teεreq-iyi tenhert.
Teεreq-ak tenhert.
Teεreq-am tenhert.
Teεreq-as tenhert.
Teεreq-aɣ tenhert.
Ad d-aɣeɣ takerrust.
Uɣeɣ-d takerrust.
Uɣeɣ-d takerrust si ssuq.
Ur d-ttaɣeɣ ara takerrust aseggas-a.
Γlayit tkeryas di Lezzayer.
Tecεel tmes di leswam n tkeryas.
Tecεel tmes di leswaq.
Kullec ɣlay.
D acu ara ččen medden?
Amek ara qableɣ?
Amek ara qableɣ ussan?
Simmal d zzyada n temsal.
Yerra s iɣẓer.
Rran s asif.
Tṣubb s anda ur d-tettali.
Yuli s anda ur d-ittrusu.
Tilufa n zzman.
Taluft tettabaε tayeḍ.
Ṛwiɣ tilufa.
Saεid bu tlufa.
Tugi ad tefru taluft-a.
Iferru tilufa n medden.
Iferru tilufa n medden, yettu iman-is.
Ur t-terzi ara taluft.

























